sequenceDiagram
    participant Kafka as Kafka Topic<br/>elpa-hint-created
    participant HintAdapter
    participant HintService
    participant HintMapper
    participant HintRepository
    participant PostgreSQL
    
    Kafka->>+HintAdapter: HintDto message
    Note over HintAdapter: @AsyncListener triggered
    HintAdapter->>+HintService: saveHints(List.of(hintDto))
    
    loop For each HintDto
        HintService->>+HintMapper: dtoToEntity(hintDto)
        HintMapper-->>-HintService: HintEntity
    end
    
    HintService->>+HintRepository: saveAll(hintEntities)
    HintRepository->>+PostgreSQL: INSERT INTO hint (...)
    PostgreSQL-->>-HintRepository: Success
    HintRepository-->>-HintService: Saved entities
    HintService-->>-HintAdapter: void
    HintAdapter-->>-Kafka: ACK